    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fabulous marine animals resembling a sea horse or equine, having two front legs and a lower body ending in a dolphin's or fish's tail. Often accompanying the chariot of Neptune and other sea deities.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
